%1s Form Thwarted By Injury

Awful luck for %1s, as he suffered a bad injury during %2s's match with %3s.\nThe %4s was looking to continue his rich vein of form, but he had to be taken off the pitch. Reports from the dressing room suggest that he will face a lengthy spell on the sidelines.
%1s Sparkles Again

%1s is a man who is very happy with his current run of form. "I'm playing really well at the moment, and really enjoying my football at %2s" he told the assembled press after the game against %3s. It certainly seems the %4s is in the team for the foreseeable future if he keeps this level of play up.
Knock effects %1s Form

%1s has been one of the best players in the league in recent matches, but sadly for fans of %2s, we might not be seeing him again for a while as he picked up a slight injury in the game against %3s.\nThe %4s %5s was looking to continue his rich vein of form, but he had to be taken from the pitch. The news from the dressing room suggested the injury was not serious and he should return after a short lay off.
%1s Fails To Continue Run Of Form

%1s is a player who has been in a great run of form lately, but his performance for %2s against %3s in their last game wasn't up to the standards he set himself lately. "Yeah, it wasn't one of my better games" he said. "I've been playing really well, and perhaps I was due a poor game. But I won't let my head drop, and I'll come back strong in the next game".
